A '''hearing enhancer''' is a small device that can be inserted in the ear to help those who are partially deaf.

It is possible to pick up the signal from a hearing enhancer and use it as a long range listening device. This was demonstrated during the [[Galactic City spaceport hostage siege]].

[[Kal Skirata]] had a hearing enhancer but usually did not use it.

